Count traffic using bash shell. Div +/- 2%

Run:
chmod 755 ./load_int_sum.sh
./load_int_sum.sh
or 
bash ./load_int_sum.sh

Output all system interface counters. Ending press 'Ctrl + C' Output summary statistics.
Exmpl:


eth0: In 1461 Out 1486
eth1: In 6681 Out 7471
eth2: In 460 Out 956
eth3: In 60 Out 60
lo: In 0 Out 0
^C
Interface: eth0 - Total in: 4958 Total out: 4950 Max in: 2770 Max out: 2196
Interface: eth1 - Total in: 10493 Total out: 11794 Max in: 6681 Max out: 7471
Interface: eth2 - Total in: 940 Total out: 1798 Max in: 460 Max out: 956
Interface: eth3 - Total in: 180 Total out: 180 Max in: 60 Max out: 60
Interface: lo - Total in: 0 Total out: 0 Max in: 0 Max out: 0
Kill catcher
 
